 recipe.","Verjuice is made using unfermented white grapes and provides a more subtle acidic hint to dishes than using lemon juice or vinegar.","You can substitute verjuice for dry white wine.","White fish and lemon are another classic flavour combination. Enjoy this risotto with a chilled glass of white wine to complement all of the flavours.","Ensure you use good quality, very fresh fish in this recipe.","Omit the optional butter to make this recipe dairy free.","Leftover risotto can be used to make Arancini balls. Search \"Arancini\" on the Recipe Community home page (recipecommunity.com.au)."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","2 portions"]}